# Cloudflare Pages Redirects

# Normalize www to non-www (301 permanent redirect)
https://www.immigronews.com/* https://immigronews.com/:splat 301!

# SPA fallback — serve index.html for any route that doesn't match a static file.
# Prerendered pages are written as dist/route.html (not dist/route/index.html)
# so CF Pages and Vercel serve them directly at the clean URL without redirect.
/* /index.html 200
